<u>08/11/2021 </u>Report amended to correct GGT value. The instrument originally reported a GGT value of 25 U/L. Given normal ALKP activities, GGT analysis was repeated to verify. Several repeat tests resulted in GGT values of <3 U/L, which is clinically normal. We apologize for this error. The cause of the original instrument error is unknown. Please know we will thoroughly evaluate the circumstances leading to this error in order to prevent recurrence. Do not hesitate to contact me with any questions.
